{"tid":1136762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】立法會法律顧問質疑修訂逃犯條例形式　函政府促解說","createTime":"2019-05-03T08:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T15:11:50.000Z","uid":241764,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9005233db1a595dfc0a3b7cb19d6e7f1556cb3c8","tid":1136762,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"立法會下周一（6日）會就修訂《逃犯條例》，再度召開法案委員會。立法會法律顧問較早時致函政府，就修訂《逃犯條例》提出多項質疑，要求政府解說。<br />\n<br />\n立法會法律顧問指出，1997年立法會曾召開法案委員會討論《逃犯條例》，當時的政府認為，與內地移交逃犯的安排應分開處理，在此後的階段再立法。法律顧問如今要求政府澄清（clarify），為何現行卻以修例，用「特別移交安排」來處理逃犯移交事宜。<br />\n<br />\n法律顧問續稱，1997年當局曾表明，一次過移交個案安排是用以補充長期雙邊協議，可藉此增加合作的司法管轄區數目，當中所有程序及保障都會繼續應用。法律顧問稱，由此可見，一次過的移交逃犯安排，是用以補充雙邊協議，一貫亦需在立法會訂立附屬法例，故要求政府說明，為何今次在3月的文件中卻稱現行安排並不可行。<br />\n<br />\n法律顧問稱，1998年保安局提交保安事務委員會的文件中，指出與中國內地訂定逃犯協議，有5項指導原則，包括應考慮「一國兩制」原則、兩地之間的法律，和司法制度差異等；法律顧問要求政府說明，5項指導原則如何應用在修例的特別移交逃犯安排中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190503/s00001/1556871019681/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F-%E5%87%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BF%83%E8%A7%A3%E8%AA%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190503%2Fs00001%2F1556871019681%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25BC%258F-%25E5%2587%25BD%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25BF%2583%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AA%25AA&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=3bc71ccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190503%2Fs00001%2F1556871019681%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25BC%258F-%25E5%2587%25BD%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25BF%2583%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AA%25AA&h=9eafe93d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190503/s00001/1556871019681/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F-%E5%87%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BF%83%E8%A7%A3%E8%AA%AA</a>"},{"pid":"bcf00acc9d9addb2d80fefde46bee57daf3b5b0a","tid":1136762,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"幫手拉布？"},{"pid":"50dd66e6bd157390072231e9c090c3b4887c985d","tid":1136762,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c9f57730c20e2e8c185c6d568ab0bdd64cb541","tid":1136762,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hoball"},{"pid":"a31480508d7f9c3053b12cdf597de82880da811c","tid":1136762,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:21:13.000Z","msg":"開始有燶味了~~林鄭今朝口風都開始轉軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9f9e9b4acc35468f62ccbe142935ee3c9c038e","tid":1136762,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"解決提出問題既人 應該會換左個法律顧問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0705daae8e09282debb8d4faf4e9517e36635d60","tid":1136762,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"蠢人治港"},{"pid":"37dbe08aef79f150d44f04960d20616fc25ae0f5","tid":1136762,"uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"立法會秘書處 (法律事務部)<br />\n法律事務部負責就法案及附屬法例擬備法律報告，並就與委員會議事程序有關的法律事宜，向立法會各個委員會提供意見。秘書處的法律顧問亦是立法機關的法律顧問，就與立法會議事程序有關的法律事宜，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">向立法會主席及立法會秘書提供意見</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n根據《基本法》第71條，立法會主席由議員互選產生。第六屆立法會主席的選舉於2016年10月12日，即新一屆立法會任期開始的首次會議上舉行，並<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">由梁君彥議員當選為第六屆立法會主席</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">梁君彥</span></strong>:修訂逃犯條例直上大會未必可取<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2115623/%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%3A%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2115623%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%253A%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258F%2596&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=d772d3a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2115623/%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%3A%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%96</a><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例】法案具爭議 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">梁君彥</span></strong>：引《議事規則》91條未必可取<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/320370/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E